  ('optometrist-moex-00660', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某人右眼裸視遠點在角膜後方20cm，若配戴頂點距離12mm之框架眼鏡，此鏡片之第一焦點及第二焦點 與角膜之相對位置為何？', '["第一焦點在角膜前22.4cm，第二焦點在角膜後20cm", "第一焦點在角膜前22.4cm，第二焦點在角膜後22.4cm", "第一焦點在角膜前20cm，第二焦點在角膜後20cm", "第一焦點在角膜前20cm，第二焦點在角膜後22.4cm"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00661', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某正視眼且絕對老花，若不考慮景深，想觀看眼前20cm物體，配戴+5.50D鏡片，其頂點距離應為多少？', '["10.2mm", "14.2mm", "16.2mm", "18.2mm"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:43+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "77d308980065", "answer_pdf_sha1": "815ebca9fd63", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
